sequenceDiagram
  title Match Result Submission (Admin)
  participant Admin as Admin User
  participant FE as Angular App
  participant API as API Gateway
  participant Mat as Matches Service
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  Admin->>FE: Open Match Detail
  FE->>API: GET /matches/{matchId}
  API->>Mat: Load match
  Mat->>DB: SELECT match + sets
  DB-->>Mat: Rows
  Mat-->>API: Match DTO
  API-->>FE: 200 { match }

  Admin->>FE: Enter scores, click Save
  FE->>API: PATCH /matches/{matchId} { sets, status }
  API->>Mat: Validate + apply result
  Mat->>DB: UPDATE match & sets; compute winner
  DB-->>Mat: OK
  Mat-->>API: Updated DTO
  API-->>FE: 200 { match }
  FE->>FE: Show success toast, refresh bracket